➜成都警方开展特巡警警务实战技能教官练兵集训
http://www.sohu.com/a/417163921_162522	82643
<p><span>来源：<span>中国新闻网</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>
<p>2020-09-09 06:56</p>
<p><i><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200909/4859995cdedc4cb491ebd076a6e36926.jpeg" /></i></p>
<p><i><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200909/99af8e37383246b0bd0f937f990cf2f1.jpeg" /></i></p>
